{"id":138897,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/简讯：北京称煽动茉莉花别有用心/","date":"2011-03-07T05:40:39Z","modified":"2011-03-07T05:40:39Z","title":"简讯：北京称煽动茉莉花别有用心","content":"<div>\n<p>北京市政府新闻办公室发言人王惠说，网上有人发动示威游行，是别有用心，希望在中国发生类似中东及北非的动乱事件。</p>\n<p>她指有关人士是打错主意，又形容这是“竹篱打水一场空”，类似情况不会及不可能在中国发生，因为中国民众并不愿意见到。</p>\n<p>她强调，外国记者在华采访，必须遵守中国的法律。</p>\n<p>对于有记者问及有外国记者在西单采访时被拘留，王惠反问记者，为何类似事件一而再，再而三发生。</p>\n<p>她问记者是在报道事实，还是在制造新闻。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/nlPzEGXyW-UYduwdBVYlYRyf_D4/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/nlPzEGXyW-UYduwdBVYlYRyf_D4/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/nlPzEGXyW-UYduwdBVYlYRyf_D4/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/nlPzEGXyW-UYduwdBVYlYRyf_D4/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=r9xfx00jWzA:286OoJ7chk4:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=r9xfx00jWzA:286OoJ7chk4:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=r9xfx00jWzA:286OoJ7chk4:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=r9xfx00jWzA:286OoJ7chk4:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=r9xfx00jWzA:286OoJ7chk4:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=r9xfx00jWzA:286OoJ7chk4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/r9xfx00jWzA\" width=\"1\" />